{"tid":616056,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"姐弟愛，牙朗姐姐：你將再次回擊質疑","createTime":"2018-04-04T00:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T04:43:00.000Z","uid":25345,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd931e0e372dda3afcd9f7c7a7bf0097160f9ff","tid":616056,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T00:52:55.000Z","msg":"自從家姐post完後牙朗就充滿力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://tu.qiumibao.com/uploads/day_180116/201801160828215769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftu.qiumibao.com%2Fuploads%2Fday_180116%2F201801160828215769.jpg&h=d29167de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC羅的姐姐卡蒂婭-阿維羅在個人社交媒體中發布了一則消息。在文中，她回憶了C羅成長中的挑戰，同時表示自己弟弟將再次回擊眼下所遭受的質疑。<br />\n<br />\n公開信全文︰<br />\n<br />\n當你12歲去裡斯本的時候，眼裡滿是淚水與希望。他們說你不過是又一個馬德拉來的孩子。結果不到5年，你就加入了葡萄牙體育一隊。<br />\n<br />\n當你第一次走進成年隊的時候，他們說你不過是又一個技術不錯的小混蛋。但幾個月後，你就和曼聯隊簽下了合約。<br />\n<br />\n當你剛到英格蘭時，人們說你不過是一筆對未來的投資，但在之後6個賽季中你打進了118個球。<br />\n<br />\n當你簽約皇家馬德裡的時候，人們說你不過是個賣球衣的把戲。而從2009年到今天，你在418場裡打進了422個球，也打破了所有你能在俱樂部打破的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n當你在2008年第一次拿到金球的時候，人們說你也就到此為止了，但你後來又拿了4個。<br />\n<br />\n而當你成為國家隊隊長時，人們說你不是個領袖，更不具領導能力。但在2016年，你帶著大家拿到了歐洲杯。<br />\n<br />\n如今，你在兩三場比賽裡沒能拿出超人的表現，人們開始說你不過是個生涯步入暮年的球員，開始走下坡路了。別擔心，當你再次拿著獎杯站上埃菲爾鐵塔頂端，或是再次打入決定性進球，打破又一項紀錄時，人們會再次將眼光聚集在你身上，他們將為你喝采。當然，你更是許多窮人的希望，你是他們唯一的明星。"},{"pid":"f37b0252f689a60756d70b4f6fed495e4b645612","tid":616056,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢姐姐咩樣"},{"pid":"c1e620cc047543651de22fe841dea82eb208e321","tid":616056,"uid":42429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:04:54.000Z","msg":"歐洲杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b1dda170d1806f996a5ac6bede02566bcaf37a","tid":616056,"uid":27163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99df54141797e6395fc9b4e5057dccced8f40e2","tid":616056,"uid":126823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f37b0252f689a60756d70b4f6fed495e4b645612","tid":616056,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢姐姐咩樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T03:29:27.000Z","msg":"牙朗咁既樣"},{"pid":"42082b675dbd66035266565336985991b5ee331d","tid":616056,"uid":118727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f37b0252f689a60756d70b4f6fed495e4b645612","tid":616056,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢姐姐咩樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T03:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/113336_d49c9e7b4c3eaee8682016adf4ae0be8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F113336_d49c9e7b4c3eaee8682016adf4ae0be8.png&h=0f92b451&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4c0f20d9299c36a2990b7be63d8e75d04322026","tid":616056,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"姐弟情萬歲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9133c99df0c0f849c59932a02df461dcdd80e9a2","tid":616056,"uid":132264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42082b675dbd66035266565336985991b5ee331d","tid":616056,"uid":118727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f37b0252f689a60756d70b4f6fed495e4b645612","tid":616056,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class